@startuml seq_mark_notification_read
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Mark Notification as Read

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "User" as User
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Noti Service" as Noti
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG
database "MongoDB" as Mongo

User -> Client : Click on Unread Notification
Client -> Gateway : PUT /api/noti_ser/announcements/:id/read
Gateway -> Noti : Route Request

Noti -> Noti : Verify JWT Token & Extract user_id

Noti -> PG : INSERT INTO announcement_reads \n(announcement_id, user_id) \nON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
Noti -> Mongo : INSERT NotificationLog \n(Action: 'READ', performed_by: user_id)

Noti -> Client : 200 OK (Marked as read)
@enduml